{"tid":2147031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【珍惜生命】男警順利紀律部隊宿舍內上吊昏迷 兒子發現報警惜反魂乏術","createTime":"2020-08-09T03:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T04:32:37.000Z","uid":35562,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0fa87a5959a0083df65ad7f8cec4bee172d92780","tid":2147031,"uid":35562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:39:50.000Z","msg":"昨晚10時許，秀茂坪順利紀律部隊宿舍，發生男警員上吊自殺案件，一名47歲姓周警員，被十多歲兒子發現在宿舍單位內以布帶上吊自殺，昏迷不醒，兒子將其解下並報警求助，救護員接報到場，將他送聯合醫院，惟經搶救後證實不治。警方正調查死者尋死原因，初步相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n今次是不足一個月內第2宗警員自殺案。上月22日，一名37歲休班警員被發現倒卧德田邨德盛樓平台，懷疑從高處跳下自殺，當場身亡。該名休班警員於7月21日涉嫌用手提電話偷拍裙底被捕，獲准保釋後即跳樓亡，故懷疑是畏罪自殺，據悉死者因患有柏金遜症影響仕途，近年一直鬱鬱不歡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200809/T6I4WDGQVYRBD63ZU5N4U7YK44/?fbclid=IwAR1Z1t-f40yKW3Krc2h2cfT3OxSzhrljlU4gN-5oYQCMt3C3uJ-8FjzDjcs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200809%2FT6I4WDGQVYRBD63ZU5N4U7YK44%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Z1t-f40yKW3Krc2h2cfT3OxSzhrljlU4gN-5oYQCMt3C3uJ-8FjzDjcs&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=5c29b632\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200809%2FT6I4WDGQVYRBD63ZU5N4U7YK44%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Z1t-f40yKW3Krc2h2cfT3OxSzhrljlU4gN-5oYQCMt3C3uJ-8FjzDjcs&h=7a8042fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200809/T6I4WDGQVYRBD63ZU5N4U7YK44/?fbclid=IwAR1Z1t-f40yKW3Krc2h2cfT3OxSzhrljlU4gN-5oYQCMt3C3uJ-8FjzDjcs</a>"},{"pid":"45bb92d7ca3c0ff0311eedb9364196e87b082048","tid":2147031,"uid":311309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:41:43.000Z","msg":"-1"},{"pid":"39a493c5be4dcbf6c235f2effdd24e152c92f15f","tid":2147031,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:44:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74a54ff41e33f527b8e6083d99eb066d6496fd4d","tid":2147031,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T03:44:16.000Z","msg":"